{
  "texts": [
    "The coders held weekly meetings to discuss insights generated throughout the analytical process, collaboratively construct meaning from the data, and promote reflexivity through conversations around the researchers' assumptions, beliefs, and backgrounds as they related to this study.",
    "Interviews were coded in Microsoft Word using the comment function to tag the data with code labels.",
    "The software R was then used to extract the comments along with the tagged data excerpts and place them into an excel spreadsheet along with the coded survey data.",
    "The codes were refined by collapsing those that shared similar underlying concepts, and eventually formed into themes and subthemes representative of the overarching relationships between codes.",
    "After an initial round of themes were developed, these themes were reviewed in relation to the broader dataset, finalized codes, and research question to ensure the interpretations and information provided addressed the original intent of the study."
  ]
}